<plot>A cinematic journey around the world covering over 40 years of surf discovery ( 1960 to present) as captured by two underground surf cinematographers Greg Weaver and Spyder Wills. Narrated by Jeff Bridges. With epic unseen super 8mm footage of surfers Gerry Lopez, Sunny Garcia, Herbie Fletcher, Stacy Peralta, Rory Russell and many other surf legends.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?100816</url></doc>
